UAL Inc, which on May 1 becomes AllegisCorp, said it established a direct communications link betweenits Apollo Services reservations system and Budget Rent a Car,Hilton Hotels and Hilton International Hotels.    Under the new system, all Budget, Hilton and HiltonInternational hotel reservations made through Apollo, which isowned by UAL's Covia Corp, will pass the ARINC system and speedup time it takes to complete a traveler's reservation, thecompany said. Reuter&#3;